== ARIEL WAYZ UMUKUBWA UKURI MUTO UFITE IJWI RITANGAJE ==
Ariel yavukiye i [[Rubavu|RUBAVU]] , mu ntara yuburengera zuba ,akaba ari umwana 

wa gatanu mumuryango wabantu [[Umunanira|umunani]]. ariel ntakidasanzwe kubona yarakuze 

akunda umuziki kuko yakuze nyina akunda kuririmba muri orchester INGERI muri 90s.

mugihe abandi banyeshuri bibandaga mugukurikirana ayandi masomo asanzwe , we

yibanze gusa m[[UMUZIKI|umuziki]] aba aribyo akurikirana nkumwuga kuko nizo zari inzozi ze.<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/entertainment/ariel-wayz-fast-rising-girl-golden-voice</ref>

== AHO YABANJE KUBARIZWA MUMUZIKI WE ==
Ariel ni umwe mubari bagize itsinda rikomeye mumuziki nya[[rwanda]] ryitwa symphony

rigizwe nabanyeshuri barangije kunyundo.

Ubu afite imyaka 19 gusa umukobwa ukuri muto afatwa nkumwe mubahanzi bafite

impano u [[Rwanda]] rufite<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/entertainment/ariel-wayz-fast-rising-girl-golden-voice</ref>.

=== IKINTU GITANGAJE Ariel ni umuhanzi kazi ukora umuziki bidatewe ===
nicyo asahaka kuwukuramo gusa awukora bitewe nicyo awumvamo. yivugirako akunda umuziki

ngo ntiyibaza ubundi buzima yaba atuyemo atari umuziki.

